name-type-step.rb

For example:
	root-test-0.rb
		performance.rb
			per1.rb
  Or
	per1-test-0.rb
	fun1-test-1.rb
	per2-test-0.rb
  And
	core-build-1.rb
	utils-build-2.rb
	tests-build-3.rb
  Finally
	core-pre-0.rb

name - whatever except '-' and your os can accept it

type - build | pre | install | test
	Or
	   b     | p   | i       | t

step - 0-9
